# galaxygearapp

Simple API to return items of gear (called Products in the API) for Rebel Fighters and Stormtroopers.
It follows the JSONAPI standard, with 'data' as the root notde of each object. Related objects are contained
in 'relationships' object nodes.

## Products Collection [/products.json]

### List All Products [GET]

Returns all products and their related objects (if they exist).

Paging is not currently supported.

#### Required:

    None.

#### Relationship objects:

    None (returned in response body).


