## Product [/products/{product_id}.json]

### View a Product [GET]



+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

### Create a New Product [POST]

Accepts a single object containing a product and two relationship objects.

#### Required:

    String: name (cannot be blank/null/empty)

#### Relationship objects:

    Category (required): the category id
    Manufacturer (optional): the manufacturer id. Can be null it not needed, eg:
    
    "manufacturer":{
        "data":null
        }
     }

+ Request (application/json)

    + Body
    
            {
               "data":{
                  "attributes":{
                     "name":"test",
                     "description":null,
                     "weight-value":null,
                     "weight-unit":null,
                     "is-shared":false,
                     "shared-capacity":null
                  },
                  "relationships":{
                     "category":{
                        "data":{
                           "type":"categories",
                           "id":"7"
                        }
                     },
                     "manufacturer":{
                        "data":{
                           "type":"manufacturers",
                           "id":"1"
                        }
                     }
                  },
                  "type":"products"
               }
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Body
    
